messages.message: Hey Austria! ~N~ Would you be down for an AR? I reckon it's a really strong alliance - I've been playing it a lot recently and love it. Do you want to DMZ or bounce in Gal?
I'm personally a fan of the bounce but I can also just agree to a DMZ if you want to play more agressive :)
Okay, let's bounce if that's your preference! I think AR is very fun!
Especially if you can focus north!

Excellent! I think it really depends on how you want to play it. If you want to open hard against Turkey then we should bounce - if you want to hedgehog against Italy then we should DMZ. What do you want to do?
Let's bounce! I like turning an AIR into an AR if possible
Awesome, bouncing!
Wow, bold move by Italy. Are you worried at all?
Do you want to bounce again or can we just DMZ it this turn?
Nah, Tyr is kind of fun. no blame!
What would War do if we DMZ?
I'd probably move it to Ukraine. I'm not sure though - do you have any thoughts?
Yeah Ukraine makes sense. Are you willing to attack Turkey soon?
I'm going to Rumania here. Are you able to get Greece?
With Sev or Ukr?
Ukraine.
Would you go to black also? Not setting up well to attack Turkey.
I think Turkey will be bouncing me again.
Oh, cool. Makes sense then
